# Welcome aboard

Hi, I'm Jeff — also known as OneWheelGeek. Code, wood, unicycles, and self-hosting. This is my capsule: a small, quiet corner of the internet served over both Gemini and the web from one little Go server.

No trackers, no JavaScript, no engagement metrics. Just text, links, and the occasional strong opinion about unnecessary cloud dependencies.

